title: Episode Nine: Kirsten Nelson - Shawn vs. the Red Phantom
description:
Hey Psycho-s! It’s Chief Vick day! On this episode we talk to Kirsten Nelson about her journey on becoming Chief Vick and joining the Psych family, what it’s like being pregnant on set, and focus on Season One Episode Eight: Shawn vs. The Red Phantom.
